title: What the hell does this mean?

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body: I put my cursor over it, but it didn't tell me what it means... What does it mean? Will my life be cut short?

replies.body:
probably just a warning that these missions expire soon. Since they are only at 2/3 you still have 1 mission after them.

But the last mission is only for like 60 tokens so dont be too worried
